high_descs: Walk forward and to the left to face the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Cut the lettuce on the center of the kitchen table into slices.
Turn around and step forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn right and step forward to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then remove it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the slice of lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To clean a slice of lettuce plus store it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your left, go toward the door, and turn right to face the counter with the microwave
Pick up the butter knife from the counter
Turn around, move across the room to the table with cabbages
Slice the middle cabbage with the knife
Turn around and go to the fridge
Open the fridge, place the knife on the top-right tray, and close the fridge
Go back to the table with the cabbages
Pick up a slice from the cut cabbage
Take the cabbage slice to the sink
Put the cabbage slice in the sink basin, run the water on it, stop the water, and pick the slice up
Go back to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the slice on the same tray with the knife, and close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a clean cabbage slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the microwave.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Cut the lettuce on the round table.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the round table.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
